WEBVTT

00:25.510 --> 00:26.280
Over there!

00:27.190 --> 00:27.760
Quick!

00:28.190 --> 00:28.920
After her!

00:29.430 --> 00:31.560
Life is like a game.

00:31.950 --> 00:34.070
No one wants to be the one who loses.

00:35.030 --> 00:35.920
So

00:36.120 --> 00:37.710
we try our hardest

00:37.990 --> 00:39.920
to reach our ideal destination.

00:43.310 --> 00:44.480
Unfortunately,

00:45.390 --> 00:46.710
fate always strikes

00:46.710 --> 00:48.350
when you least expect it,

00:49.200 --> 00:52.000
delivering an absurd ending
beyond imagination.

01:16.200 --> 01:21.210
[Love Between Lines]

01:22.150 --> 01:24.480
[Episode 1]

01:29.680 --> 01:31.039
I already sent the document Mr. Xu wanted

01:31.039 --> 01:33.039
to him at 7:30 this morning.

01:33.789 --> 01:35.920
If there are any details
that need to be discussed or adjusted,

01:35.920 --> 01:37.350
just contact Shao.

01:37.600 --> 01:39.710
The restaurant is booked for 4:30 PM,

01:39.710 --> 01:41.960
and I've also left Shao's number
as the contact.

01:41.960 --> 01:44.509
Yes, I asked for leave a month ago.

01:45.200 --> 01:47.530
I'll definitely invite you to my wedding.

01:47.840 --> 01:48.400
Goodbye.

01:49.150 --> 01:50.680
Ms. Hu, this is it.

01:49.410 --> 01:50.979
[Engagement Banquet
Zhang Qiran & Hu Xiu]

01:51.120 --> 01:51.789
Thank you.

01:51.789 --> 01:52.720
You're welcome.

01:57.759 --> 01:58.479
Xiu.

01:58.479 --> 01:58.920
You look so beautiful today.

01:58.920 --> 01:59.840
Thanks.

02:00.760 --> 02:02.430
Auntie, can I borrow your phone?

02:02.430 --> 02:03.150
You've grown so tall.

02:03.150 --> 02:05.150
Look at him—always clinging to you.

02:05.230 --> 02:05.760
Congratulations.

02:05.760 --> 02:06.840
Thank you. Thank you.

02:06.840 --> 02:07.630
Thank you.

02:08.919 --> 02:09.320
Xiu.

02:09.320 --> 02:10.110
Auntie.

02:10.280 --> 02:11.510
Sorry I'm late.

02:11.510 --> 02:13.770
It's okay. Young people are always busy.

02:13.880 --> 02:15.740
Qiran hasn't arrived yet either.

02:17.070 --> 02:19.600
You've got quite a few relatives.
I don't know any of them.

02:19.600 --> 02:21.600
You'll get to know them soon enough.

02:21.720 --> 02:22.920
Your mother and the others are over there.

02:22.920 --> 02:24.250
I'll go over there then.

02:26.320 --> 02:26.880
Okay.

02:27.440 --> 02:28.110
Congratulations.

02:28.110 --> 02:29.110
Thank you, Uncle.

02:30.480 --> 02:31.070
Mom.

02:31.280 --> 02:32.390
Why are there three tables now?

02:32.390 --> 02:34.070
And this wasn't the hall I booked.

02:34.070 --> 02:35.800
I've calculated with your dad.

02:35.880 --> 02:37.000
Since we were having the event anyway,

02:37.000 --> 02:39.390
and Qiran's mother had also
invited quite a few relatives

02:39.390 --> 02:40.920
who've all come from far away,

02:40.920 --> 02:42.160
we added one table.

02:42.160 --> 02:43.510
The cost for upgrading the hall

02:43.510 --> 02:44.920
is covered by your father.

02:44.920 --> 02:46.450
He likes lively occasions.

02:46.480 --> 02:48.540
He was more than happy to pay for this.

02:50.000 --> 02:52.400
I really don't know what to do
with you guys.

02:56.040 --> 02:57.790
How could you bring your laptop here?

02:57.790 --> 02:59.200
You worked overtime
until past 2 AM this morning.

02:59.200 --> 03:00.260
Isn't that enough?

03:01.070 --> 03:03.730
I'm just worried
there might be some emergency.

03:04.110 --> 03:05.880
What's that bulging thing you're carrying?

03:05.880 --> 03:07.210
Gripping it so tightly.

03:07.350 --> 03:08.680
The wedding gift money.

03:10.040 --> 03:12.880
No matter how much money
Qiran's family offers today,

03:12.880 --> 03:14.280
our family will match it.

03:15.280 --> 03:16.390
Our amount

03:16.390 --> 03:18.250
definitely won't exceed theirs.

03:18.390 --> 03:19.520
When the time comes,

03:19.790 --> 03:21.280
we'll offer slightly less than them,

03:21.280 --> 03:22.610
just about this number.

03:22.790 --> 03:24.280
Anyway, in the end, all this gift money

03:24.280 --> 03:26.110
will go to you two as a newlywed couple.

03:26.110 --> 03:26.760
Mom.

03:28.320 --> 03:29.160
Why do you think

03:29.160 --> 03:30.040
your father and I

03:30.040 --> 03:31.510
insisted on splitting
the engagement banquet costs

03:31.510 --> 03:33.670
with their family all this time?

03:34.630 --> 03:36.160
It wasn't for anything else

03:36.200 --> 03:38.390
but that you could have
confidence and footing

03:38.390 --> 03:40.160
in this relationship in the future.

03:40.160 --> 03:41.420
Do you understand now?

03:53.950 --> 03:54.510
Hu Xiu,

03:54.670 --> 03:55.550
please reply to my message.

03:55.550 --> 03:56.920
What's wrong with you, Hu Xiu?

03:56.920 --> 03:58.720
Don't want to work here anymore?

03:59.790 --> 04:01.250
I already asked for leave.

04:07.550 --> 04:09.230
C-Could you call Qiran again?

04:09.230 --> 04:10.690
Okay, I'll call him again.

04:12.790 --> 04:14.450
Why hasn't Qiran arrived yet?

04:14.720 --> 04:16.850
Everyone's asking where the groom is.

04:16.990 --> 04:18.750
He's not responding to my messages

04:18.750 --> 04:20.190
and not answering his phone.

04:20.190 --> 04:23.250
Look, your mother and Qiran's mother
are both worried.

04:23.280 --> 04:23.720
Mom.

04:23.820 --> 04:24.580
Xiu.

04:25.400 --> 04:26.960
Why hasn't Qiran arrived yet?

04:26.960 --> 04:28.160
He's still not answering his phone.

04:28.160 --> 04:29.990
Could something have happened to him?

04:29.990 --> 04:30.670
Don't worry, Auntie.

04:30.670 --> 04:32.400
I'll call his colleague to ask.

04:33.740 --> 04:36.340
You don't want me to play?
I won't listen to you.

04:39.520 --> 04:40.159
Hu Xiu.

04:41.040 --> 04:42.040
Let's break up.

04:43.600 --> 04:45.080
I won't attend the engagement banquet.

04:45.080 --> 04:45.750
From now on,

04:45.920 --> 04:47.850
I won't return to Shanghai either.

04:47.990 --> 04:49.120
Don't try to find me.

04:50.110 --> 04:50.920
Let's each live our own lives.

04:50.920 --> 04:52.310
What's going on?

04:54.750 --> 04:55.550
I know, right?

04:55.550 --> 04:56.990
It's so inappropriate.

04:56.990 --> 04:58.190
This won't do, right?

05:00.460 --> 05:04.170
[One month later]

05:11.430 --> 05:12.790
Xiu, I'm coming in.

05:13.640 --> 05:15.600
I went out of my way
to buy almond cakes today.

05:15.600 --> 05:17.520
From that shop near our junior high.

05:17.520 --> 05:19.380
Weren't you always craving them?

05:19.520 --> 05:20.600
Come out and eat.

05:25.790 --> 05:27.870
You didn't even touch this bowl of noodles
from yesterday.

05:27.870 --> 05:29.190
The soup has dried up.

05:30.990 --> 05:32.790
Can't you give me some response?

05:34.790 --> 05:35.960
Are you still alive?

05:39.600 --> 05:40.550
I am.

05:41.159 --> 05:42.220
Get up and check in.

05:45.720 --> 05:46.430
Smile.

05:49.550 --> 05:50.700
Mrs. Bai, don't worry.

05:50.700 --> 05:52.810
She's fine with me here.

05:53.280 --> 05:54.280
You live too far away.

05:54.280 --> 05:56.810
Don't trouble yourself
going back and forth.

05:56.990 --> 05:58.750
Why don't I just
change into different outfits?

05:58.750 --> 06:00.280
You can take several at once

06:00.350 --> 06:01.670
and send one over every day.

06:01.670 --> 06:04.000
Then you won't have to run between places.

06:04.720 --> 06:07.250
It's been a month already.
Still feeling sad?

06:08.960 --> 06:10.840
It's not that bad.

06:10.840 --> 06:11.640
It's just that

06:12.040 --> 06:14.170
I don't feel motivated to do anything.

06:14.750 --> 06:15.600
Anyway,

06:15.990 --> 06:18.230
I've saved up so many vacation days
in 3 years of work.

06:18.230 --> 06:19.490
I might as well just...

06:20.160 --> 06:21.890
I found something for you to do.

06:22.080 --> 06:23.640
I guarantee it'll get you motivated.

06:23.640 --> 06:24.840
What's this?

06:25.870 --> 06:28.310
A large-scale immersive virtual reality
murder mystery game.

06:28.310 --> 06:29.520
It's been super popular lately.

06:29.520 --> 06:30.920
It's right near our shop.

06:31.870 --> 06:33.040
We can still catch the last session.

06:33.040 --> 06:34.440
Quick, get up and change.

06:36.310 --> 06:38.159
Escape from reality.

06:36.690 --> 06:38.730
[Welcome to the dreamy journey
to escape from reality]

06:42.310 --> 06:43.170
Thank you, sir.

06:43.430 --> 06:44.520
Hurry, we're running out of time.

06:44.520 --> 06:45.380
We've arrived?

06:45.600 --> 06:46.130
Let's go.

06:46.550 --> 06:47.430
Hurry up.

06:48.550 --> 06:49.550
Zhao.

06:50.520 --> 06:51.430
Slow down.

06:56.430 --> 06:58.440
There are two of us.
Can we still catch the last session?

06:58.440 --> 07:00.040
It starts in 30 minutes.

07:00.080 --> 07:01.230
After you pay,

07:01.230 --> 07:03.630
our staff will take you
to change costumes.

07:03.870 --> 07:04.920
It's 600 yuan per person.

07:04.920 --> 07:06.190
With the coupon, it's 20% off.

07:06.190 --> 07:07.400
That's 480 yuan.

07:08.160 --> 07:09.600
480...

07:10.750 --> 07:11.790
I'll pay.

07:14.230 --> 07:14.920
Done.

07:15.110 --> 07:16.040
960?

07:16.150 --> 07:17.670
You two can choose the bags

07:17.670 --> 07:18.990
according to your preferences.

07:18.990 --> 07:21.040
Inside the bags are your identity cards
for Rongcheng

07:21.040 --> 07:22.240
and important props.

07:22.790 --> 07:23.720
Quick, pick one.

07:24.190 --> 07:25.480
I'll take this one then.

07:25.480 --> 07:27.230
There's a separate changing area inside.

07:27.230 --> 07:29.890
You can only enter the game area
after changing.

07:29.920 --> 07:31.190
I'd like to remind everyone

07:31.190 --> 07:32.310
that when changing,

07:32.310 --> 07:33.990
check your identity cards.

07:34.520 --> 07:36.480
Players belong to 4 different factions.

07:36.480 --> 07:39.280
Each of you has someone to assist,

07:39.280 --> 07:41.990
to help them become the new mayor.

07:42.750 --> 07:43.520
Our game

07:43.520 --> 07:45.350
is entirely virtual reality interactive.

07:45.350 --> 07:47.340
So please wear your glasses properly.

07:47.340 --> 07:48.930
We wish you all

07:49.050 --> 07:50.909
a pleasant evening in Rongcheng.

07:52.170 --> 07:53.220
We've arrived in Rongcheng.

07:53.220 --> 07:56.280
Players, please exit the vehicle
in an orderly manner.

08:02.960 --> 08:04.190
I'm the wife of the richest man,

08:04.190 --> 08:05.350
assisting the Police Chief.

08:05.350 --> 08:06.210
What about you?

08:07.790 --> 08:10.050
Haven't you checked your identity card?

08:11.040 --> 08:11.990
Not yet.

08:12.110 --> 08:13.470
This game has no script.

08:13.490 --> 08:15.230
Only these few clues on the cards.

08:15.230 --> 08:16.400
The plot development
entirely depends on

08:16.400 --> 08:18.860
the interactions between players and NPCs.

08:19.190 --> 08:20.310
This is it?

08:20.480 --> 08:22.540
It's all dark. There's nothing here.

08:23.110 --> 08:24.430
You haven't put your glasses on yet.

08:24.430 --> 08:25.890
Put them on and take a look.

08:37.789 --> 08:39.240
How did they do this?

08:56.880 --> 08:57.340
This...

08:58.000 --> 08:58.600
This is...

08:59.470 --> 09:01.670
No wonder the tickets are so expensive.

09:11.210 --> 09:14.380
♪ I'll be relentless ♪

09:15.730 --> 09:18.780
♪ The terror in your dreams ♪

09:20.780 --> 09:24.030
♪ My ghost surrounds you ♪

09:25.190 --> 09:26.710
Everyone, welcome to Rongcheng.

09:25.360 --> 09:28.030
♪ And never lets you sleep ♪

09:27.640 --> 09:29.000
The blizzard has blocked the roads.

09:29.000 --> 09:30.240
I apologize for the inconvenience,

09:30.240 --> 09:31.920
but you'll have to rest
in Rongcheng for now.

09:30.280 --> 09:33.030
♪ I'm never giving up ♪

09:33.160 --> 09:34.400
I must remind you all

09:34.590 --> 09:35.670
that Rongcheng is a dangerous place

09:34.930 --> 09:37.490
♪ I'm never letting go ♪

09:35.920 --> 09:37.720
filled with all sorts of people.

09:37.760 --> 09:39.160
If you let your guard down,

09:39.160 --> 09:39.830
I'm afraid

09:40.070 --> 09:41.400
you might never return.

09:41.550 --> 09:42.550
Whether you can board the train

09:42.550 --> 09:43.790
leaving Rongcheng

09:44.590 --> 09:46.320
depends on your own abilities.

09:48.000 --> 09:49.040
Dangerous?

09:53.790 --> 09:54.880
Don't worry.

09:55.040 --> 09:56.880
I know you can't handle horror games.

09:56.880 --> 09:58.070
This isn't a horror one.

09:58.070 --> 09:58.600
Let's go.

10:09.160 --> 10:10.280
I really regret it.

10:10.670 --> 10:12.930
I should have eaten that bowl of noodles.

10:13.640 --> 10:14.240
What?

10:14.950 --> 10:15.590
Nothing.

10:17.040 --> 10:19.040
This city looks just like a real one.

10:20.000 --> 10:21.880
This is even more realistic
than a hologram.

10:21.880 --> 10:22.830
The online reviews
weren't exaggerating at all.

10:22.830 --> 10:23.640
What's wrong?

10:24.550 --> 10:25.430
Nothing.

10:26.000 --> 10:27.390
I've played murder mystery games

10:27.390 --> 10:28.640
at company outings before,

10:28.640 --> 10:31.220
but the buildings here
are much more thoughtfully designed.

10:31.220 --> 10:33.230
[Qianghua Xingye Ltd.]

10:32.280 --> 10:35.120
The designers must have referenced
a lot of real-world locations.

10:35.120 --> 10:36.190
Of course.

10:36.310 --> 10:38.920
Otherwise, it wouldn't
have caught my attention.

10:38.920 --> 10:39.450
Alright,

10:39.950 --> 10:41.750
let's meet at the hotel up ahead.

10:43.120 --> 10:44.050
It's right here.

10:45.520 --> 10:47.950
Distinguished guests,
your rooms are ready.

10:47.950 --> 10:49.400
If you need anything,

10:49.670 --> 10:51.120
you can come to me. I'm Bai Luoyu.

10:49.980 --> 10:51.440
[Bai Luoyu, Owner of Central Hotel,
Rongcheng Intelligence Center]

10:53.470 --> 10:54.070
Thank you.

10:54.670 --> 10:56.190
How long does this game last?

10:56.190 --> 10:57.070
Four hours.

10:57.470 --> 10:58.400
Four hours?

10:59.400 --> 11:00.400
That's 120 yuan per hour,

11:00.400 --> 11:01.550
2 yuan per minute.

11:01.550 --> 11:02.760
So to get our money's worth,

11:02.760 --> 11:04.400
we need to stick it out till the end.

11:04.400 --> 11:05.000
Good luck.

11:05.880 --> 11:07.880
Then I'll sleep some of it off first.

11:14.950 --> 11:16.680
This bed is quite comfortable.

11:21.190 --> 11:22.070
Rongcheng is under martial law.

11:22.070 --> 11:23.550
All guests, open
your doors immediately

11:23.550 --> 11:25.120
and cooperate with the search!

11:25.120 --> 11:26.050
Open up! Open up!

11:27.400 --> 11:28.730
Room 107, open the door!

11:32.760 --> 11:35.430
Sun Jiaying, overseas PhD in chemistry.

11:35.670 --> 11:37.950
You have a package of opium
worth a fortune,

11:37.950 --> 11:40.000
but it's contraband in Rongcheng.

11:40.310 --> 11:41.310
If found, you'll face imprisonment...

11:41.310 --> 11:42.400
If you don't open up and cooperate,

11:42.400 --> 11:43.430
we'll have to break in!

11:43.430 --> 11:43.890
Open up!

11:47.360 --> 11:48.470
What kind of bad luck is this?

11:48.470 --> 11:50.470
Even in a game, I'm still so unlucky.

12:15.470 --> 12:16.520
-Stop!
-Stop!

12:16.830 --> 12:17.880
Open your bag! What are you doing?

12:17.880 --> 12:18.240
Stop!

12:18.360 --> 12:19.160
Open your bag!

12:19.520 --> 12:21.520
Why are you running so fast? Open it!

12:34.360 --> 12:35.690
What are you looking at?

13:07.940 --> 13:09.460
Are you an NPC?

13:10.700 --> 13:12.150
It's okay if I

13:12.460 --> 13:13.460
eat a prop, right?

13:26.470 --> 13:28.400
Would you like to cooperate, Miss?

13:31.360 --> 13:32.710
C-Cooperate on what?

13:33.310 --> 13:35.000
In Rongcheng, there are
various ways to play.

13:35.000 --> 13:35.950
What resources do you have,

13:35.950 --> 13:37.360
or what do you need?

13:37.670 --> 13:38.710
Tell me and let's see

13:38.710 --> 13:40.310
if we can help each other out.

13:42.400 --> 13:43.000
I see.

13:43.630 --> 13:45.560
Then please help me take this away.

13:45.640 --> 13:46.520
I'm exhausted.

13:46.520 --> 13:47.710
I just want to sit quietly for a while.

13:47.710 --> 13:49.510
I don't want to be chased around.

13:50.830 --> 13:51.640
The female players I meet

13:51.640 --> 13:53.310
are all idiots.

13:54.630 --> 13:55.510
What was that?

13:56.120 --> 13:56.760
I said

13:56.880 --> 13:57.790
this item

13:58.530 --> 13:59.460
is too valuable.

13:59.650 --> 14:01.950
I need to think about
what I can offer in exchange for this.

14:01.950 --> 14:03.150
Let me think about it.

14:05.740 --> 14:07.600
Wasn't it still here a moment ago?

14:10.790 --> 14:11.790
A quarter ago,

14:12.070 --> 14:13.670
the mayor was assassinated.

14:13.880 --> 14:15.520
Rongcheng is under martial law.

14:15.520 --> 14:16.360
Everyone

14:16.460 --> 14:18.150
must cooperate with the search.

14:18.150 --> 14:18.910
Search them!

14:20.190 --> 14:21.810
[Influential on both sides of the law]

14:20.190 --> 14:21.810
[Ning Zechen, Police Chief,
Mayor Candidate]

14:25.530 --> 14:25.940
You...

14:26.080 --> 14:26.860
I've made up my mind.

14:26.860 --> 14:27.770
Deal's off.

14:28.110 --> 14:29.970
Staying alive is more important.

14:32.690 --> 14:34.090
It's just 480 yuan.

14:34.110 --> 14:35.310
Arrest me if you want.

14:42.240 --> 14:43.170
Chief Ning.

14:48.640 --> 14:49.880
Ms. Sun and I have been here

14:49.880 --> 14:51.400
all evening catching up.

14:51.710 --> 14:52.840
She's not a suspect,

14:53.230 --> 14:53.870
right?

14:59.190 --> 15:00.810
Even with someone vouching for her,

15:00.810 --> 15:02.340
we still have to search her.

15:14.740 --> 15:16.070
You dare lay a hand on me?

15:16.310 --> 15:17.430
You've crossed the line!

15:17.430 --> 15:18.490
Don't fight. Um...

15:18.770 --> 15:20.070
The mayor and I...

15:23.830 --> 15:26.090
Ms. Sun, take your time. There's no rush.

15:29.230 --> 15:30.500
I have nothing to do

15:30.910 --> 15:32.240
with the mayor's death.

15:33.330 --> 15:35.930
Chief Ning, if you're so fond of
body searches,

15:36.080 --> 15:37.510
does that also include me

15:38.190 --> 15:39.390
and my people as well?

15:44.060 --> 15:46.470
These people are really immersed in
their characters.

15:46.470 --> 15:47.620
Who are you really?

15:50.390 --> 15:54.030
[Qin Xiaoyi, Warlord Commander,
as cunning as a fox, deep and complex]

15:55.190 --> 15:57.470
I just went to the bathroom

15:57.950 --> 15:59.680
and missed all the excitement.

16:01.240 --> 16:01.920
Chief Feng.

16:02.430 --> 16:03.690
Why are you here as well?

16:03.690 --> 16:07.670
[Fabulously wealthy, wary and suspicious]

16:03.690 --> 16:07.670
[Feng Youjin, Minister of Finance]
[Mayor Candidate]

16:08.310 --> 16:09.910
The mayor was assassinated,

16:10.120 --> 16:12.710
so I came to get details from General Qin.

16:13.280 --> 16:14.520
General Qin?

16:15.000 --> 16:17.330
You're from the Military Affairs Office?

16:17.670 --> 16:19.730
Well, I've just taken up my position.

16:20.310 --> 16:22.170
Chief Ning, it's understandable

16:22.590 --> 16:24.880
that you're a bit anxious
for Rongcheng's safety.

16:24.880 --> 16:27.470
It's just Ms. Sun
has just returned from abroad.

16:27.470 --> 16:28.950
Forcing a body search like that

16:28.950 --> 16:30.710
isn't exactly proper hospitality.

16:30.710 --> 16:31.550
That's right.

16:31.920 --> 16:33.830
Ms. Sun is a person of importance.

16:34.000 --> 16:35.710
I was just about to invite her

16:35.710 --> 16:37.570
to visit the Ministry of Finance.

16:37.830 --> 16:38.550
Chief Ning.

16:38.710 --> 16:40.000
When you have solid evidence,

16:40.000 --> 16:41.920
you can arrest Ms. Sun then.

16:43.520 --> 16:45.320
Chief Feng, are you trying to...

16:45.430 --> 16:46.630
Take her away from me?

16:48.800 --> 16:50.630
Why is he looking at me?

16:58.670 --> 17:00.270
Who would you like to go with?

17:02.640 --> 17:03.710
I...

17:06.160 --> 17:08.640
This General looks more capable.

17:08.640 --> 17:09.569
I'll go with you.

17:28.800 --> 17:30.710
Why didn't you go with Feng Youjin?

17:30.710 --> 17:31.840
Why

17:31.990 --> 17:33.160
should I go with him?

17:37.230 --> 17:38.230
Thank you.

17:39.710 --> 17:41.440
And thank you for the hawthorn.

17:42.600 --> 17:43.460
It was nothing.

17:49.010 --> 17:50.250
Qin Xiaoyi,

17:50.450 --> 17:52.510
you've been waiting here for me
on purpose, haven't you?

17:52.510 --> 17:53.950
I've been waiting for you
for quite a while.

17:53.950 --> 17:54.950
You were too slow.

17:55.270 --> 17:56.990
But catching me won't do you any good,

17:56.990 --> 17:58.230
because I don't

17:58.230 --> 17:59.360
have anything on me.

17:59.990 --> 18:00.800
Is that so?

18:08.050 --> 18:09.050
What about this?

18:14.880 --> 18:15.750
Everyone

18:15.990 --> 18:17.640
must cooperate with the search.

18:17.640 --> 18:18.370
Search them.

18:19.950 --> 18:20.990
I've made up my mind.

18:20.990 --> 18:22.080
Deal's off.

18:22.430 --> 18:24.290
Staying alive is more important.

18:26.670 --> 18:27.920
What key is this?

18:28.270 --> 18:30.470
The key to the secret room
in the former mayor's house.

18:30.470 --> 18:31.330
He wanted to stay alive,

18:31.330 --> 18:32.940
so he tried to frame you.

18:33.190 --> 18:33.950
Ms. Sun,

18:34.950 --> 18:37.010
what do you plan to do with this opium?

18:37.080 --> 18:38.270
This is contraband.

18:38.800 --> 18:39.660
You can take it.

18:41.360 --> 18:43.490
It's indeed contraband in Rongcheng,

18:43.950 --> 18:45.030
but it's harmless

18:45.800 --> 18:46.880
here with me.

18:47.640 --> 18:49.710
I only focus on what I want.

18:51.710 --> 18:52.510
Ms. Sun,

18:53.670 --> 18:55.640
do you know what you want?

18:56.360 --> 18:56.800
I...

19:02.270 --> 19:02.930
Move along.

19:04.160 --> 19:04.880
Hurry.

19:04.990 --> 19:05.990
I know how to walk.

19:09.210 --> 19:13.510
♪ Under the streetlight,
I grow increasingly weary ♪

19:14.030 --> 19:16.600
After graduation, I'll definitely
go study architecture abroad.

19:15.660 --> 19:20.500
♪ A few specks of dust
drift by in the wind ♪

19:16.920 --> 19:17.950
When I return after completing my studies,

19:17.950 --> 19:19.750
I'll have you all live in houses I design.

19:19.750 --> 19:20.600
Let's eat.

19:20.600 --> 19:21.750
Let's eat first. Come on.

19:21.750 --> 19:22.190
Come on, let's eat.

19:22.190 --> 19:23.230
Dad, do you not believe me?

19:22.600 --> 19:26.760
♪ The girl who once
basked in the sunlight ♪

19:23.230 --> 19:23.990
I do.

19:24.120 --> 19:24.920
I believe you.

19:25.030 --> 19:26.090
Come on, let's eat.

19:27.430 --> 19:29.430
Mom, I'll go to the hospital
right away.

19:27.620 --> 19:30.540
♪ Where did she go to play? ♪

19:30.430 --> 19:32.070
The plan of studying abroad can wait.

19:30.980 --> 19:33.950
♪ I don't understand either ♪

19:32.140 --> 19:34.070
Let's get Dad's leg treated first.

19:36.190 --> 19:40.020
♪ Flicking through old chat logs ♪

19:38.120 --> 19:38.880
Mr. Xu,

19:39.470 --> 19:40.470
I want to transfer

19:40.560 --> 19:41.670
to the design department.

19:41.670 --> 19:43.160
Go get me a cup of coffee.

19:42.270 --> 19:47.150
♪ I just realized the replies
were somewhat delayed ♪

19:43.920 --> 19:46.750
I just want to live a simple life.

19:47.320 --> 19:48.710
Zhang Qiran would be perfect.

19:48.290 --> 19:54.280
♪ At the crossroads of choices,
amidst the bustling crowd ♪

19:49.400 --> 19:50.030
Hu Xiu.

19:50.950 --> 19:51.990
Let's break up.

19:55.520 --> 20:02.790
♪ Who hasn't paid the price
and still fallen short? ♪

20:00.560 --> 20:02.160
When have I ever truly gotten

20:02.810 --> 20:07.360
♪ Stand with me tonight,
look at the starlight ♪

20:04.670 --> 20:06.430
what I wanted?

20:08.170 --> 20:14.210
♪ Even if we're always
pushed aside by reality ♪

20:09.640 --> 20:10.880
Can't I win once

20:13.230 --> 20:14.880
even in a game?

20:14.900 --> 20:21.120
♪ I know how hard it is to push forward ♪

20:21.660 --> 20:30.000
♪ But there are always people
in this world trying again like me ♪

20:23.670 --> 20:25.670
Opium can be exchanged for diamonds.

20:25.670 --> 20:26.640
Send it to the headquarters,

20:26.640 --> 20:27.800
obtain the documents,

20:27.800 --> 20:30.260
and repay Chief Feng
who you're indebted to.

20:32.270 --> 20:34.930
No wonder he thought
I'd leave with Feng Youjin.

20:56.670 --> 20:57.560
I finally found you.

20:57.560 --> 20:59.020
Quick, give me some money.

20:59.640 --> 21:00.430
Just this?

21:00.770 --> 21:01.570
And these too.

21:05.400 --> 21:06.920
Where did you get so much money?

21:06.920 --> 21:07.780
Just earned it.

21:07.800 --> 21:09.130
Take as much as you want.

21:10.360 --> 21:10.920
Hello.

21:10.920 --> 21:12.670
Can I come to you for any kind of request?

21:12.670 --> 21:13.270
Of course.

21:14.800 --> 21:15.670
Opium...

21:15.670 --> 21:16.600
How do I sell it?

21:17.230 --> 21:18.800
Dealing with opium is too much trouble.

21:18.800 --> 21:21.460
It's not just a matter of
one or two gold coins...

21:21.640 --> 21:22.770
How much do you need?

21:22.950 --> 21:25.640
The black market in Rongcheng
is at the porcelain shop.

21:25.640 --> 21:26.430
Put your goods in

21:26.430 --> 21:28.160
the blue and white porcelain
on the second row

21:28.160 --> 21:29.430
and wait outside for 15 minutes.

21:29.430 --> 21:30.890
Someone will take the item

21:31.080 --> 21:32.510
and leave what you need.

21:35.270 --> 21:36.600
Hello, are you a player?

21:37.270 --> 21:38.120
We're players too.

21:38.120 --> 21:39.560
Do you know where this is?

21:40.510 --> 21:41.160
Turn from here.

21:41.160 --> 21:41.950
Over there, right?

21:41.950 --> 21:43.210
-Thank you.
-Let's go.

21:48.400 --> 21:49.920
The opium is gone.

21:50.160 --> 21:51.620
So where are the diamonds?

21:51.710 --> 21:52.430
Boss.

21:52.540 --> 21:54.200
Has anyone been here just now?

21:54.360 --> 21:55.230
No one.

21:55.640 --> 21:57.230
Who took my opium?

22:00.880 --> 22:02.560
You didn't want it
when I offered it for free,

22:02.560 --> 22:04.560
and now you come here sneaking around?

22:04.560 --> 22:06.490
Give me back my opium and diamonds!

22:13.260 --> 22:19.390
[Post Office]

22:14.270 --> 22:16.600
I should wait here for the reply, right?

22:18.120 --> 22:19.250
Hello. Your letter.

22:22.190 --> 22:23.080
Thank you.

22:24.070 --> 22:24.860
This...

22:29.750 --> 22:30.710
Final mission:

22:30.880 --> 22:33.220
deliver the chemical formula
to the contact.

22:33.220 --> 22:36.080
This will help Chief Feng
win the position of mayor.

22:37.830 --> 22:38.980
So that's how it is.

22:43.930 --> 22:45.730
Mission exposed. Act quickly.

22:44.790 --> 22:46.620
[Mission exposed, act quickly.
Rongcheng Square. Blue scarf.]

22:45.920 --> 22:47.780
Rongcheng Square. Blue scarf.

23:07.510 --> 23:08.470
It's you.

23:08.710 --> 23:10.320
So you're the contact?

23:12.270 --> 23:12.900
Sit.

23:16.470 --> 23:17.510
Give me the item,

23:17.780 --> 23:19.710
and your mission will be complete.

23:30.550 --> 23:32.590
Why is he also wearing a blue scarf?

23:37.080 --> 23:38.880
Your mission seems to have been exposed.

23:38.880 --> 23:40.040
Who you want to trust

23:40.400 --> 23:41.360
is up to you.

23:43.360 --> 23:44.160
Actually,

23:44.880 --> 23:47.480
you've already had an answer
to this question.

23:50.910 --> 23:52.910
You were the one who saved me before.

23:54.120 --> 23:55.190
To be precise,

23:55.320 --> 23:57.360
I saved you from Ning Zechen's gun

23:57.430 --> 23:59.090
and almost got myself killed.

24:00.120 --> 24:01.640
So Chief Ning and I...

24:01.950 --> 24:03.480
You're not on the same side.

24:04.220 --> 24:05.380
When you're alert,

24:05.920 --> 24:07.580
you're actually quite smart.

24:10.880 --> 24:13.210
Why doesn't that sound like a compliment?

24:16.800 --> 24:18.430
Now Chief Feng and Chief Ning

24:18.430 --> 24:20.360
are competing for the position of mayor.

24:20.360 --> 24:22.090
You and I are naturally allies.

24:27.030 --> 24:27.840
I trust you.

24:31.560 --> 24:32.990
Thank you for your hard work, Ms. Sun.

24:32.990 --> 24:34.390
You made the right choice

24:34.640 --> 24:35.330
and

24:35.600 --> 24:37.060
executed it brilliantly.

24:38.470 --> 24:40.800
Can't let you save the wrong person,
can I?

24:43.710 --> 24:45.910
I'm done for. They're here to arrest me.

25:06.940 --> 25:11.490
♪ Close your eyes for me ♪

25:08.510 --> 25:09.710
Your mission is complete,

25:09.710 --> 25:10.850
but the danger isn't over.

25:10.850 --> 25:11.600
Go to the train station now.

25:11.600 --> 25:13.120
You must leave Rongcheng alive.

25:13.020 --> 25:15.190
♪ Don't rush to wake up ♪

25:15.660 --> 25:18.880
♪ Before the night ends ♪

25:21.760 --> 25:27.080
♪ Will you stay with me? ♪

25:24.800 --> 25:25.800
Thank you,

25:26.520 --> 25:27.710
General Qin.

25:28.000 --> 25:30.000
♪ I won't search for ♪

25:30.800 --> 25:33.610
♪ The reason we met ♪

25:35.840 --> 25:36.390
Stop!

25:36.920 --> 25:37.640
Quick! After her!

25:37.380 --> 25:41.650
♪ We will meet tomorrow ♪

25:39.270 --> 25:40.320
Stop right there,

25:40.500 --> 25:42.260
or we'll shoot!

25:42.940 --> 25:43.940
♪ I know ♪

25:44.270 --> 25:44.990
Stop there!

25:44.850 --> 25:49.130
♪ Oh, special night ♪

25:47.080 --> 25:47.750
Stop!

25:52.250 --> 25:56.130
♪ Oh, special night ♪

25:57.020 --> 25:58.410
How could this be?

26:04.010 --> 26:05.800
Sun Jiaying, an overseas student,

26:05.800 --> 26:07.080
has been eliminated after death.

26:07.080 --> 26:09.000
When my glasses go black,

26:09.430 --> 26:10.560
that means I'm dead?

26:10.760 --> 26:11.360
Yes.

26:11.600 --> 26:13.470
Our equipment has a trigger system.

26:13.470 --> 26:14.880
Since you triggered the death ending,

26:14.880 --> 26:17.410
the device has
automatically disconnected.

26:20.990 --> 26:21.400
I...

26:21.520 --> 26:23.450
I'm not the first one who died, am I?

26:25.710 --> 26:27.230
Who killed me?

26:27.540 --> 26:29.070
Those two killers in black?

26:29.710 --> 26:32.320
In Rongcheng, your opponent could be...

26:33.080 --> 26:33.840
Anyone.

26:35.430 --> 26:36.270
I've already lost,

26:36.270 --> 26:38.130
and you won't even let me know why.

26:38.320 --> 26:38.990
Many players

26:38.990 --> 26:39.990
play through multiple times.

26:39.990 --> 26:41.840
Not only can you experience
flexible storylines,

26:41.840 --> 26:44.230
but our virtual settings
also change frequently,

26:44.230 --> 26:46.470
ensuring something fresh every time.

26:49.710 --> 26:51.080
They're all so rich?

26:51.400 --> 26:52.880
After the entire game ends,

26:52.880 --> 26:54.270
all players will gather here

26:54.270 --> 26:55.400
for a review session.

26:55.400 --> 26:57.660
You'll get key information at that time.

27:07.800 --> 27:08.560
Hu Xiu.

27:09.190 --> 27:10.320
Are you home?

27:10.510 --> 27:12.670
Your apartment is leaking water
into my apartment again,

27:12.670 --> 27:13.510
you know?

27:15.080 --> 27:17.190
Zhao, I have to go now.

27:20.240 --> 27:23.560
♪ You thought I'd fall and lose my way ♪

27:25.070 --> 27:28.890
♪ Thought I'd never find the strength
to stay♪

27:31.340 --> 27:34.640
♪ But every time I'm defeated ♪

27:35.720 --> 27:38.300
♪ I stood back up and held the line ♪

27:38.740 --> 27:41.210
♪ Winters don't bother me ♪

27:41.520 --> 27:47.960
♪ I'm stronger than I used to be ♪

27:45.230 --> 27:46.430
Mr. Xiao.

27:49.010 --> 27:52.380
♪ Now watch me fight ♪

27:52.510 --> 27:57.730
♪ Oh, I'm done pretending ♪

27:52.640 --> 27:54.300
Mr. Xiao, we're leaving then.

27:57.750 --> 27:59.510
♪ And I ♪

27:59.710 --> 28:02.310
♪ I'm ready, I won't hide ♪

28:02.340 --> 28:04.840
♪ Now it's my turn ♪

28:05.480 --> 28:08.340
♪ The reality is boring ♪

28:08.370 --> 28:11.690
♪ Following all the rules ♪

28:11.710 --> 28:15.430
♪ I'll be the one writing my own story ♪

28:18.400 --> 28:20.230
That Chen Dabao downstairs
from your place,

28:20.230 --> 28:21.830
I think he's just malicious.

28:22.190 --> 28:24.030
Didn't the community already
assess the situation?

28:24.030 --> 28:25.560
The leak is his own problem.

28:26.320 --> 28:27.320
By the way, I left in a hurry yesterday,

28:27.320 --> 28:28.800
and I didn't get to hear the game review.

28:28.800 --> 28:29.400
In the end,

28:29.840 --> 28:30.900
did Chief Feng win?

28:31.270 --> 28:32.930
It was that Qin Xiaoyi who won.

28:33.930 --> 28:34.370
Qin...

28:35.600 --> 28:36.430
Qin Xiaoyi?

28:37.710 --> 28:38.670
Wasn't he just playing

28:38.670 --> 28:39.950
an NPC in the storyline?

28:39.950 --> 28:41.710
How could he have become the mayor?

28:41.710 --> 28:43.560
He wasn't just an ordinary NPC.

28:43.560 --> 28:45.080
They said there were 4 factions in total,

28:45.080 --> 28:47.010
and he was the leader of one of them.

28:47.430 --> 28:48.270
What?

28:49.230 --> 28:50.080
But I was

28:50.080 --> 28:51.840
busy winning money at the casino
the whole time,

28:51.840 --> 28:53.230
so I didn't see how they played.

28:53.230 --> 28:54.560
I only heard the review.

28:54.750 --> 28:57.400
They said his storyline
was hidden quite deep.

29:02.080 --> 29:03.280
Not just our faction,

29:04.640 --> 29:05.470
even Ning Zechen's people

29:05.470 --> 29:07.200
were taken down by Feng Youjin.

29:07.880 --> 29:09.360
I was quite committed in this game.

29:09.360 --> 29:11.760
Looks like we're definitely going to lose.

29:13.800 --> 29:14.800
Not necessarily.

29:15.430 --> 29:16.600
[Post Office]

29:16.560 --> 29:18.880
If Feng Youjin can't get the formula
from her,

29:18.880 --> 29:19.800
he can't win.

29:20.320 --> 29:21.510
That Qin Xiaoyi

29:21.510 --> 29:22.950
saw Feng Youjin's

29:22.950 --> 29:25.120
contact note and props before I did.

29:31.040 --> 29:31.990
I believe you.

29:35.030 --> 29:35.920
Thank you,

29:36.840 --> 29:37.920
General Qin.

29:38.710 --> 29:39.840
Then he concealed his identity,

29:39.840 --> 29:41.640
obtained the formula documents,

29:41.640 --> 29:44.510
and finally led his faction to victory.

29:45.320 --> 29:46.400
The formula?

29:46.510 --> 29:48.080
He took my formula.

29:48.080 --> 29:49.790
He should have given it to Feng Youjin.

29:49.790 --> 29:50.940
What formula?

29:52.670 --> 29:53.710
He clearly said

29:53.710 --> 29:55.600
he was on the same side as me.

30:03.200 --> 30:04.560
You all probably don't know this.

30:04.560 --> 30:06.120
When Qin Xiaoyi executes an enemy,

30:06.120 --> 30:07.230
he fires two shots

30:07.230 --> 30:08.360
to ensure the target's dead.

30:08.360 --> 30:08.920
Two shots?

30:08.920 --> 30:09.840
Who knows how cool that is?

30:09.840 --> 30:10.800
So manly.

30:17.470 --> 30:18.270
Liar.

30:19.030 --> 30:20.470
He was trying to kill me to silence me,

30:20.470 --> 30:21.950
and there I was like an idiot,

30:21.950 --> 30:22.560
saying

30:22.560 --> 30:23.490
thank you to him.

30:26.570 --> 30:27.700
Where are you going?

30:28.990 --> 30:31.110
In real life, there are too many people
I can't deal with.

30:31.110 --> 30:32.660
But at least in this game,

30:32.920 --> 30:35.450
I'll make anyone who crosses me
pay the price.

30:49.470 --> 30:51.330
Everyone, welcome to Rongcheng.

30:52.080 --> 30:53.470
The blizzard has blocked the roads.

30:53.470 --> 30:54.840
I apologize for the inconvenience,

30:54.840 --> 30:56.430
but you'll have to rest
in Rongcheng for now.
